OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy announces his cancer is terminal
OL,6,FIn an interview with The Sunday Times,
OL,7,Fhe announced that he has prostate
OL,8,Fcancer and it's terminal.
OL,10,FHe said that he went to the doctor
OL,11,Flast September because he thought he
OL,12,Fhad strained his shoulder lifting
OL,13,Fweights.
OL,15,FA tumour was found in his shoulder,
OL,16,Fand a second scan found the primary
OL,17,Fcancer in his prostate, which had
OL,18,Fmetastasised to his bones. He has
OL,19,Ftumours in his shoulder, pelvis, hip,
OL,20,Fspine and rib.
