OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy announces his cancer is terminal
OL,6,FHe told the newspaper: "As unnatural
OL,7,Fas it feels, this is nature."
OL,9,FHe added: "You know, we were all born
OL,10,Fand we all die, and this is just part
OL,11,Fof the process.
OL,13,F"You remind yourself, aren't I lucky
OL,14,Fthat there is medicine I can take that
OL,15,Fwill fend this off for as long as
OL,16,Fpossible."
