OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy announces his cancer is terminal
OL,6,FThe Olympic legend also revealed how
OL,7,Fhis wife, Sarra, was diagnosed with
OL,8,F"very active and aggressive" multiple
OL,9,Fsclerosis just a month or so after he
OL,10,Fwas found to have terminal cancer.
OL,12,FA scan just before Christmas confirmed
OL,13,Fthat Sarra needed urgent treatment.
OL,15,FThe pair have been married since 2010
OL,16,Fand have two children, aged seven and
OL,17,Ften.
OL,19,FHoy, originally from Edinburgh, asked
OL,20,Ffor privacy back in February following
OL,21,Fhis announcement.
