OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy announces his cancer is terminal
OL,6,FHe wrote: "I have a bit of news. Last
OL,7,Fyear I was diagnosed with cancer,
OL,8,Fwhich came as a huge shock, having had
OL,9,Fno symptoms up to that point."
OL,11,FThe Scot said: "I'm optimistic,
OL,12,Fpositive and surrounded by love for
OL,13,Fwhich I'm truly grateful. As you might
OL,14,Fimagine, the last few months have been
OL,15,Fincredibly difficult. However, I
OL,16,Fcurrently feel fine."
