OL,3,CSix-time Olympic champion Sir Chris
OL,4,CHoy announces his cancer is terminal
OL,6,FHoy was such a dominant force in
OL,7,Fsprint cycling that he had won six
OL,8,FOlympic, 11 world and 34 World Cup
OL,9,Ftitles by the time he retired from
OL,10,Fcompetitive racing in 2013.
OL,12,FHe is the third most-decorated British
OL,13,FOlympian of all time, with six career
OL,14,Fgolds and one silver medal.
